                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">VISUAL NOVELS</span>
                  <h4>Ren'Py</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Perfect for story-driven games. Write your narrative, add images, and you're done. Great for first-timers.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://twinery.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-svg" style="background: #59BB59;">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 7 8" fill="white"><path d="M 0,0 3,0 3,8 0,8 Z"/><path d="M 0,6.5 C 0,1 7,1 7,1 V 4 C 7,4 3,4 3,6.5 V 8 H 0 Z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">TEXT ADVENTURES</span>
                  <h4>Twine</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Create interactive fiction with zero coding. Just write your story and connect the branches.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://bitsy.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-svg" style="background: #6767b2;">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80" fill="white"><path d="M10,20 20,20 20,30 30,30 30,20 40,20 40,50 60,50 60,80 50,80 50,70 30,70 30,80 20,80 20,60 10,60z"/><path d="M60,40 70,40 70,50 60,50z"/><path d="M70,20 80,20 80,40 70,40z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">TINY GAMES</span>
                  <h4>Bitsy</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Make small, charming games in a simple tile-based editor. Perfect for atmospheric experiences.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://gdevelop.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #4B5DC4;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gdevelop.png" alt="GDevelop" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">NO CODE</span>
                  <h4>GDevelop</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Visual game builder with drag-and-drop events. Great for platformers and action games without coding.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-category">
          <h3 class="category-title intermediate">Intermediate</h3>
          <div class="resource-grid">
            <a href="https://godotengine.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-svg" style="background: #478CBF;">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M9.5598.683c-1.096.244-2.1812.5831-3.1983 1.0951.023.8981.081 1.7582.199 2.6323-.395.253-.81.47-1.178.766-.375.288-.7581.564-1.0971.9011-.6781-.448-1.3962-.869-2.1352-1.2411C1.3532 5.6934.608 6.6186 0 7.6546c.458.7411.936 1.4352 1.4521 2.0942h.014v6.3565c.012 0 .023 0 .035.003l3.8963.376c.204.02.364.184.378.3891l.12 1.7201 3.3994.242.234-1.587c.03-.206.207-.358.415-.358h4.1114c.208 0 .385.152.415.358l.234 1.587 3.3993-.242.12-1.72a.4196.4196 0 01.378-.3891l3.8954-.376c.012 0 .023-.003.035-.003v-.5071h.002V9.7498h.014c.516-.659.994-1.3531 1.4521-2.0942-.608-1.036-1.3541-1.9611-2.1512-2.8192-.739.372-1.4571.793-2.1352 1.2411-.339-.337-.721-.613-1.096-.901-.369-.296-.7841-.5131-1.1781-.7661.117-.8741.175-1.7342.199-2.6323-1.0171-.512-2.1012-.851-3.1983-1.095-.438.736-.838 1.533-1.1871 2.3121-.414-.069-.829-.094-1.2461-.099h-.016c-.417.005-.832.03-1.2461.099-.349-.779-.749-1.576-1.1881-2.3121l.001-.001zM6.4765 9.9889c1.2971 0 2.3492 1.0511 2.3492 2.3482s-1.052 2.3482-2.3492 2.3482c-1.296 0-2.3482-1.051-2.3482-2.3482 0-1.297 1.0511-2.3482 2.3482-2.3482zm11.049 0c1.296 0 2.3482 1.0511 2.3482 2.3482s-1.0511 2.3482-2.3482 2.3482-2.3492-1.051-2.3492-2.3482c0-1.297 1.051-2.3482 2.3492-2.3482zm-10.824.9301c-.861 0-1.559.698-1.559 1.5591s.698 1.5582 1.559 1.5582c.8611 0 1.5592-.698 1.5592-1.5582 0-.86-.697-1.559-1.5591-1.559zm10.598 0c-.8611 0-1.5582.698-1.5582 1.5591s.697 1.5582 1.5581 1.5582c.8611 0 1.5592-.698 1.5592-1.5582 0-.86-.697-1.559-1.5592-1.559zm-5.2985.453c.417 0 .757.308.757.6871v2.1622c0 .379-.339.687-.757.687s-.756-.308-.756-.687V12.059c0-.379.339-.687.756-.687zM1.4601 16.9464c.002.377.006.789.006.871 0 3.7014 4.6944 5.4795 10.5269 5.5005h.014c5.8325-.02 10.5259-1.7991 10.5259-5.5004 0-.084.005-.495.007-.871l-3.5023.338-.121 1.729a.421.421 0 01-.389.3901l-4.1814.296a.4203.4203 0 01-.415-.358l-.238-1.6141h-3.3863l-.238 1.6141a.4192.4192 0 01-.4451.357l-4.1513-.296c-.208-.015-.375-.181-.389-.389l-.12-1.7292-3.5044-.337z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">RECOMMENDED</span>
                  <h4>Godot</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Open source, lightweight, and powerful. Great documentation, active community. Our top pick for 2D games.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.yoyogames.com/gamemaker" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-svg" style="background: #8BC34A;">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M.012 11.994 12.006 0l11.982 12.006h-6.831l-5.163-5.151-5.151 5.151 5.163 5.151v-5.151h5.151v6.903L12.006 24z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">2D FOCUSED</span>
                  <h4>GameMaker</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Industry-proven for 2D games. Free tier available. Made Undertale, Hyper Light Drifter, and more.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://love2d.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-svg" style="background: #E74A8E;">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 128 128" fill="white"><path d="M64 0c35.323 0 64 28.677 64 64s-28.677 64-64 64S0 99.323 0 64 28.677 0 64 0Zm-.074 98.715-.023.013h.045zm0 0c55.886-32.209 29.426-58.095 16.754-61.13-8.49-2.032-14.024 3.276-16.754 7.004-2.73-3.728-8.265-9.036-16.754-7.004C34.5 40.619 8.038 66.506 63.926 98.715Z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">LUA</span>
                  <h4>LÖVE</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Lightweight framework for 2D games in Lua. Simple, fast, and great for retro-style games.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-category">
          <h3 class="category-title advanced">Advanced</h3>
          <div class="resource-grid">
            <a href="https://unity.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-svg" style="background: #222;">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="m12.9288 4.2939 3.7997 2.1929c.1366.077.1415.2905 0 .3675l-4.515 2.6076a.4192.4192 0 0 1-.4246 0L7.274 6.8543c-.139-.0745-.1415-.293 0-.3675l3.7972-2.193V0L1.3758 5.5977V16.793l3.7177-2.1456v-4.3858c-.0025-.1565.1813-.2682.318-.1838l4.5148 2.6076a.4252.4252 0 0 1 .2136.3676v5.2127c.0025.1565-.1813.2682-.3179.1838l-3.7996-2.1929-3.7178 2.1457L12 24l9.6954-5.5977-3.7178-2.1457-3.7996 2.1929c-.1341.082-.3229-.0248-.3179-.1838V13.053c0-.1565.087-.2956.2136-.3676l4.5149-2.6076c.134-.082.3228.0224.3179.1838v4.3858l3.7177 2.1456V5.5977L12.9288 0Z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">INDUSTRY STANDARD</span>
                  <h4>Unity</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Massive asset store, tons of tutorials. Great for 3D. Free for small projects.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.unrealengine.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-svg" style="background: #0E1128;">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="white"><path d="M12 0a12 12 0 1012 12A12 12 0 0012 0zm0 23.52A11.52 11.52 0 1123.52 12 11.52 11.52 0 0112 23.52zm7.13-9.791c-.206.997-1.126 3.557-4.06 4.942l-1.179-1.325-1.988 2a7.338 7.338 0 01-5.804-2.978 2.859 2.859 0 00.65.123c.326.006.678-.114.678-.66v-5.394a.89.89 0 00-1.116-.89c-.92.212-1.656 2.509-1.656 2.509a7.304 7.304 0 012.528-5.597 7.408 7.408 0 013.73-1.721c-1.006.573-1.57 1.507-1.57 2.29 0 1.262.76 1.109.984.923v7.28a1.157 1.157 0 00.148.256 1.075 1.075 0 00.88.445c.76 0 1.747-.868 1.747-.868V9.172c0-.6-.452-1.324-.905-1.572 0 0 .838-.149 1.484.346a5.537 5.537 0 01.387-.425c1.508-1.48 2.929-1.902 4.112-2.112 0 0-2.151 1.69-2.151 3.96 0 1.687.043 5.801.043 5.801.799.771 1.986-.342 3.059-1.441Z"/></svg>
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">AAA QUALITY</span>
                  <h4>Unreal Engine</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Stunning visuals out of the box. Blueprint visual scripting makes it approachable. Free to use.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Programming Frameworks -->
    <section class="section section-alt" id="frameworks">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Programming Frameworks</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">For coders who prefer writing code over visual editors. Libraries and frameworks for various languages.</p>

        <div class="resource-category">
          <h3 class="category-title intermediate">Cross-Platform</h3>
          <div class="resource-grid">
            <a href="https://www.monogame.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #1a1a2e;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/monogame.png" alt="MonoGame" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">C#</span>
                  <h4>MonoGame</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Open source C# framework. Spiritual successor to XNA. Made Celeste, Stardew Valley, and more.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://libgdx.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #E74B2F;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/libgdx.png" alt="libGDX" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">JAVA</span>
                  <h4>libGDX</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Cross-platform Java game framework. Deploy to desktop, Android, iOS, and web from one codebase.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.raylib.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #191919;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/raylib.png" alt="raylib" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">C/C++</span>
                  <h4>raylib</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Simple and easy-to-use library for game programming. Great for learning. Bindings for 50+ languages.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-category">
          <h3 class="category-title rust">Rust</h3>
          <div class="resource-grid">
            <a href="https://bevyengine.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #232326;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/bevy.png" alt="Bevy" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">ECS</span>
                  <h4>Bevy</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Data-driven game engine in Rust. Fast compile times, ECS architecture. Growing rapidly.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://macroquad.rs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #3776AB;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/macroquad.png" alt="Macroquad" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">SIMPLE</span>
                  <h4>Macroquad</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Simple Rust game library inspired by raylib. Compiles to WASM. Great for jam games.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="resource-category">
          <h3 class="category-title web">Web & Scripting</h3>
          <div class="resource-grid">
            <a href="https://phaser.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #1D1F24;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/phaser.png" alt="Phaser" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">JAVASCRIPT</span>
                  <h4>Phaser</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Fast 2D HTML5 game framework. Huge community, tons of examples. Perfect for web games.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.pygame.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #306998;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/pygame.png" alt="Pygame" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">PYTHON</span>
                  <h4>Pygame</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Classic Python game library. Easy to learn, great for prototypes. Huge learning community.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://kaboomjs.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #6BC96D;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/kaboom.png" alt="Kaboom" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">JAVASCRIPT</span>
                  <h4>Kaboom.js</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Fun and fast JavaScript game library. Simple API, great docs. Perfect for quick prototypes.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Art & Graphics -->
    <section class="section" id="art">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Art & Graphics</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Free assets and tools for creating visuals.</p>

        <div class="resource-category">
          <h3 class="category-title assets">Free Assets</h3>
          <div class="resource-grid">
            <a href="https://pixabay.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-svg" style="background: #2EC66D;">
