                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">IMAGES</span>
                  <h4>Pixabay</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Millions of free images, illustrations, and vectors. No attribution required.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://opengameart.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #F7931E;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/opengameart.ico" alt="OpenGameArt" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">GAME ASSETS</span>
                  <h4>OpenGameArt</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>Sprites, tilesets, and art specifically made for games. Various licenses, check each asset.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://kenney.nl/assets" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
              <div class="card-header">
                <span class="resource-logo resource-logo-img" style="background: #FF6B6B;">
                  <img src="/images/logos/kenney.ico" alt="Kenney" />
                </span>
                <div>
                  <span class="resource-badge">CC0</span>
                  <h4>Kenney Assets</h4>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p>High-quality game assets, all public domain. Sprites, 3D models, UI elements, and more.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://itch.io/game-assets/free" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-card">
